S.FORM: Morocan Itiniay i Ruisui Cen no Hualien ko Morocan a niyaro', 161 ko sa'osi no parod no loma', 389 ko sa'osi no tamdaw. 66% ko ka'aloman no Yincomin , polong han i, 256 ko tamdaw; o roma sato i, 34% ko ka'aloman no roma a finacadan, polong han i, 133 ko tamdaw. O pa-sin-to no ka'aloman no tamdaw no kasafinacadan i, ko Amis 58%, Tayal 1%, Bunun 5%, roma 2%.
